70#define AM_HAL_SCARD_DIR_MSB 0x3F //(H)LHHL LLL LLH, state L encodes value 1, msb
71#define AM_HAL_SCARD_DIR_LSB 0x3B //(H)LHHL HHH LLH, state H encodes value 1, lsb

78#define AM_HAL_SCARD_T0_BIT_TA1_MASK (1 << 4)
79#define AM_HAL_SCARD_T0_BIT_TB1_MASK (1 << 5)
80#define AM_HAL_SCARD_T0_BIT_TC1_MASK (1 << 6)
81#define AM_HAL_SCARD_T0_BIT_TD1_MASK (1 << 7)
82
83#define AM_HAL_SCARD_TA1_PRESENCE(T0) (((T0) & AM_HAL_SCARD_T0_BIT_TA1_MASK) == AM_HAL_SCARD_T0_BIT_TA1_MASK)
84#define AM_HAL_SCARD_TB1_PRESENCE(T0) (((T0) & AM_HAL_SCARD_T0_BIT_TB1_MASK) == AM_HAL_SCARD_T0_BIT_TB1_MASK)
85#define AM_HAL_SCARD_TC1_PRESENCE(T0) (((T0) & AM_HAL_SCARD_T0_BIT_TC1_MASK) == AM_HAL_SCARD_T0_BIT_TC1_MASK)
86#define AM_HAL_SCARD_TD1_PRESENCE(T0) (((T0) & AM_HAL_SCARD_T0_BIT_TD1_MASK) == AM_HAL_SCARD_T0_BIT_TD1_MASK)
87
88#define AM_HAL_SCARD_HISTORY_LEN(T0) ((T0)&0x0F)
89

133#define AM_HAL_SCARD_TBiP1_PRESENCE(TDi) (((TDi) & AM_HAL_SCARD_TDi_BIT_TBiP1_MASK) == AM_HAL_SCARD_TDi_BIT_TBiP1_MASK)
134#define AM_HAL_SCARD_TCiP1_PRESENCE(TDi) (((TDi) & AM_HAL_SCARD_TDi_BIT_TCiP1_MASK) == AM_HAL_SCARD_TDi_BIT_TCiP1_MASK)
135#define AM_HAL_SCARD_TDiP1_PRESENCE(TDi) (((TDi) & AM_HAL_SCARD_TDi_BIT_TDiP1_MASK) == AM_HAL_SCARD_TDi_BIT_TDiP1_MASK)
